title: Fusion Delay / Flanger / Vintage Ensemble (Used)
description:
Erica Synths Fusion Delay/Flanger/Vintage Ensemble module is a distinct multifunctional analogue effects module. It combines BBD chip based effects with an adjustable tube overdrive in the delay output and a feedback path for extra thickness of the sound.

This used unit is in great shape and comes with the original box and ribbon cable.
